data.description: You must see this well maintained, well loved, two story home backing to greenspace (to be verified by buyer) and a view of farmland. You will love the spacious great room with a stone fireplace and raised hearth that is filled with windows and a gorgeous view. The kitchen has upgraded varied height cabinets and the breakfast area is bright, cheery and welcoming. Upstairs you will find an unexpectedly large loft area that could be used as a 4th bedroom if needed. The generous Primary bedroom with ensuite has a raised vanity with granite top, tiled shower and garden tub. All the sizeable secondary bedrooms won't disappoint. Loaded with big closets, tons of storage space and floored attic space (pull down stairs). The covered rear porch is the perfect place to start or end the day. Come and make this beautiful home your own!
